@startuml rules-lifecycle
title Eligibility RuleSet Lifecycle

[*] --> Draft : Logic defined by Policy Analyst

Draft --> Requested : Submitted for Governance Review
Requested --> Reviewed : Peer/Expert Review Complete

state Reviewed {
  [*] --> PendingActivation
}

Reviewed --> Active : Vertical Owner Approves Rollout
Active --> Deprecated : Replaced by New Version
Deprecated --> Archived : Historical Retention

Active --> Suspended : Policy Hold (Emergency)

@enduml
